---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About — Rank Labs">

<section class="pt-32 pb-20 px-6">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <div class="text-sm text-cyan-300 font-mono mb-4">OUR STORY</div>
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">About <span class="gradient-text">Rank Labs</span></h1>

    <!-- Josiah -->
    <div class="gradient-border rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-10 mb-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-start">
      <img src="/josiah.jpeg" alt="Josiah — Co-founder of Rank Labs" class="w-32 h-32 md:w-40 md:h-40 rounded-xl object-cover shrink-0" />
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-1">Josiah</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-cyan-300 mb-3">Co-founder & Platform Engineer</p>
        <div class="space-y-3 text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            Josiah is a Lead SRE Engineer at Disney, where he designs and builds the platforms
            that power Disney's AI integrations at scale.
          </p>
          <p>
            He built Rank Labs' entire infrastructure — from the AI agent pipeline to the Kubernetes
            cluster, automated deployment system, and SEO crawling engine. His platform engineering
            background ensures every customer site runs on battle-tested infrastructure.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Palloma -->
    <div class="gradient-border rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-10 mb-16 flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-start">
      <img src="/palloma.jpeg" alt="Palloma — Co-founder of Rank Labs" class="w-32 h-32 md:w-40 md:h-40 rounded-xl object-cover shrink-0" />
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-1">Palloma</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-cyan-300 mb-3">Co-founder & Marketing Strategist</p>
        <div class="space-y-3 text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            Palloma runs <strong class="text-white">One Take Wonder Marketing</strong> — a marketing
            and media placement company that helps businesses grow. For years, she hired outside
            agencies to handle SEO for her clients. The results? Spotty at best. Inconsistent
            deliverables, vague reports, and pricing that never matched the output.
          </p>
          <p>
            Her marketing expertise defined what SEO success actually looks like. She designed
            the formula — every check, every metric, every report section is based on what real
            businesses need to grow. She reviews every product decision through the lens of the
            business owner, not the engineer.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- The Story -->
    <div class="gradient-border rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-10 mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">How It Started</h2>
      <div class="space-y-3 text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          They built Rank Labs together. Palloma's marketing expertise defined what SEO success
          actually looks like. Josiah's platform engineering experience made it automated,
          consistent, and AI-driven. The result: a formula that covers everything SEO demands —
          and puts real updates in the hands of the customer, every single week.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">The Formula</h2>
      <p class="text-muted mb-8">
        Every site that enters the Rank Labs system goes through the same proven formula:
        crawl → analyze → optimize → create → repeat. AI handles the heavy lifting at every
        stage — crawling thousands of pages, identifying gaps, drafting content, and tracking
        rankings. You get the results without the agency overhead.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Why a Lab?</h2>
      <p class="text-muted mb-4">
        Agencies rely on manual processes. Manual processes are slow, inconsistent, and expensive.
        A lab runs experiments at scale. Our AI runs the equivalent of a full SEO team's weekly
        output — every single day — starting at $599/month.
      </p>
      <p class="text-muted mb-8">
        You still get human oversight and final approval on everything. The AI does the work.
        You make the calls. That's the formula.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">The Tech Stack</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-8">
        {[
          { label: 'Hosting', value: 'Cloudflare Pages (Global Edge)' },
          { label: 'Crawler', value: 'Custom AI Crawler Engine' },
          { label: 'Content', value: 'LLM-Powered Research & Writing' },
          { label: 'Monitoring', value: 'Prometheus + Grafana' },
          { label: 'Deployment', value: 'GitOps with Argo CD' },
          { label: 'Infrastructure', value: 'Kubernetes (k3s)' },
        ].map((item) => (
          <div class="bg-surface rounded-lg p-4">
            <div class="text-xs text-cyan-400 mb-1">{item.label}</div>
            <div class="text-sm">{item.value}</div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Based in Florida</h2>
      <p class="text-muted">
        Proudly operating from the Sunshine State. We serve businesses across the US —
        from local shops to national brands.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</Layout>
